= Appendix B — Laboratory Equipment

#hm-note[
  Equipment requirements are cumulative — Year Two students require all of Year One equipment plus Year Two additions. Year Three students require all prior equipment plus Year Three additions. Where alternatives exist, the more accessible option is noted. Students in restricted jurisdictions (e.g., those who cannot legally own laboratory glassware commercially) should contact the headmaster before beginning Month 3.
]

